title: Mem Reduct 3.1.1454 Portable
description:
Manage And Clean Your System Memory

Mem Reduct is a real-time memory management application that enables you to monitor and clean system memory on your computer.
The program uses internal Windows system features (Native API) to clear the system memory cache (system working set, working set, standby page lists, modified page lists) which forces Windows to release any memory that is no longer in use.
Other features include an option to tweak the regions of memory to be cleaned (advanced users), an automatic cleaning option once a custom threshold is reached, and a dynamic tray icon that displays the current percentage of memory in use.
Just like other memory cleaners, Mem Reduct will not magically boost your computer performance, however it does help with freeing up memory that other applications may have left in use, which will temporarily make more memory available for other applications.
